insert into Dictionary values ("220","fr","Mode","The default mode is normal. Display the lower help section for an explanation of other modes.","The accumulated mode applies to temporal histograms and is used to total the values that appear in the charts from year to year. This graphic mode allows the study of tendencies in growth or otherwise of the reports and effects. The Superimpose/Overwrite  Mode applies to event temporal or geographic temporal histograms and superimposes in one bar all the values represented."," "); /*220-Graph-Mode*/
